The invention relates to a comprehensive mechanized coal mining method through a cantilever support, which organically combines a shearer, a scraper conveyer, a cantilever support and a hydraulic breaking-off prop for combined operation. The shearer is started to cut the coal wall, and the cut-off coal automatically falls on the scraper conveyer; the scraper conveyer is started to automatically convey the coal out; when the shearer cuts the coal wall to a certain depth, an expansion link of a jack is pushed to extend out, the hydraulic breaking-off prop is used as a fixed fulcrum, and the scraper conveyer and the shearer arranged thereon are together pushed towards the coal wall; the hydraulic breaking-off prop is disassembled and separated from a top plate, a piston rod of the jack is pushed to draw back, the scraper conveyer is used as the fixed fulcrum, and the hydraulic breaking-off prop is pulled forwards; and the cantilever support moves forwards through a hydraulic operating mechanism till the cantilever support completely moves forwards in place. The comprehensive mechanized coal mining method has the advantages that the thin seam mining difficulty and the labor intensity of workers are reduced, and the mechanization degree of the thin seam mining is improved.
